PrecisREGULATIONS RESPECTING THE COORDINATION BY FEDERAL AUTHORITIES OF ENVIRONMENTAL ASSESSMENT PROCEDURES AND REQUIREMENTS which ensure that a federal environmental assessment is efficiently coordinated among federal authorities, that the process is more timely and predictable and will reduce the likelihood of more that one assessment being done for a project.
